data.description: Welcome to 13 Cambridge Dr, a charming residence nestled in the heart of Twickenham, Rome, GA. This meticulously crafted home offers a perfect blend of modern convenience and classic comfort. Here's your opportunity to own a piece of tranquility in a vibrant neighborhood. The living space on the main level is characterized by an open concept design with hardwood floors featuring a vaulted ceiling that creates a bright and airy atmosphere. The corner kitchen, with its island and stylish white cabinets, is a chef's dream. A separate office space on this level adds practicality, offering privacy for work or study. The main level also has a spacious primary suite, complete with a large bathroom designed for ultimate relaxation. An additional bedroom and bath provide comfortable space for family or guests. Heading upstairs, you'll find a generously sized bedroom with its own private bathroom, providing flexibility and comfort. This home boasts a two-car garage in the basement. The basement also has a large unfinished space for potential customization and a finished fourth full bath for added convenience. The outdoor living spaces are equally enticing, with a wrap-around porch allowing you to enjoy the picturesque surroundings. Situated on a corner lot, this home provides additional privacy and a sense of space. This residence is not just a house; it's a haven of comfort and style. From the inviting living spaces to the practical amenities, every detail has been thoughtfully considered. Don't miss the chance to make 13 Cambridge Dr your new home sweet home in Twickenham.
